reviewText: Boys still watch them at 9 & 11 years old.  Fun, quirky characters, and lively.
My kids absolutely love Geronimo!! The oldest has all the books and has read them over and over...
Geronimo does it again! Just what we expected, like all the other DVDs. My kids have watched it over and over and will watch it again.
my grandsons, 4 and 6, love watching this one!  Glad I splurged on the price and got it for them.
